{"tid":540070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今次係高鐵定動車] [威過德、日]行駛中高鐵安徽起火 1,400乘客大雪中緊急疏散","createTime":"2018-01-25T06:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T16:48:29.000Z","uid":51271,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ae01fa77634d09df3cd8c75c9ba5970f8ff0c8","tid":540070,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57752214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57752214&d=0o5azslwCYS4FXC%2BZHkPggCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a332e3b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57752214&h=b964c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57752214</a><br />\n<br />\n今日一列從山東青島開往浙江杭州的高鐵，行駛至安徽省滁州市期間，第二節車廂着火，火勢相當猛烈，列車在暴雪中緊急在當地的定遠縣停車，1,400名乘客慌張逃生，紛紛爬上月台。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的是G281次列車，有列車上的乘客指出今日約11時半，列車行駛時車廂便着火冒煙，但列車的人員沒有馬上停車，而是繼續開行至定遠站才疏散乘客。現場拍到的片段顯示，高鐵冒出濃濃黑煙，更冒出火光。<br />\n<br />\n鐵道部門指出，這列高鐵有16個車廂，共載有1,400人，事故是2號車廂的電器設備發生故障冒煙，事故未造成傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516860632_752d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516860632_752d.jpg&h=035518cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516858954_7acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516858954_7acb.jpg&h=3ccaf176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516861225_7b50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516861225_7b50.jpg&h=29f806d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516861227_58b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516861227_58b3.jpg&h=27423784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b702cf801000531a4ba72fef7d0b7c2e7e54ed8","tid":540070,"uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"CRH3，今次又燒幾十個億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c36c6511c8ff1da5c90c1aa0f6edf08c7439234","tid":540070,"uid":3063,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"多難興邦"},{"pid":"ee3af50633b4da1334f0c6fa19692aea32225b32","tid":540070,"uid":92178,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0a1787a0a0b18a36614883bdca4bc225778e87f","tid":540070,"uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 民國復興<br />\n<br />\n咁都燒你唔死"},{"pid":"9f3b1439f337483bbcaef0f65ee6623537174dee","tid":540070,"uid":68028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"有請小鳳姐"},{"pid":"b7e68e40f73e355b1701ca86e738a1991f9fd7f3","tid":540070,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"610b2e01f38ade20a29150075135fe580b5818f2","tid":540070,"uid":34949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b43195ea3fd95aecba46c086c0962533c8fef2a","tid":540070,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor