if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然飛機耐唔耐都燒鋪大<br />\n<br />\n但全電動鐵路都燒到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚7"},{"pid":"564b36398fa9c21001a58564dd8cbec4035c0d23","tid":540070,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee3af50633b4da1334f0c6fa19692aea32225b32","tid":540070,"uid":92178,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d2ae01fa77634d09df3cd8c75c9ba5970f8ff0c8","tid":540070,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57752214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57752214&d=0o5azslwCYS4FXC%2BZHkPggCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a332e3b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57752214&h=b964c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57752214</a><br />\n<br />\n今日一列從山東青島開往浙江杭州的高鐵，行駛至安徽省滁州市期間，第二節車廂着火，火勢相當猛烈，列車在暴雪中緊急在當地的定遠縣停車，1,400名乘客慌張逃生，紛紛爬上月台。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的是G281次列車，有列車上的乘客指出今日約11時半，列車行駛時車廂便着火冒煙，但列車的人員沒有馬上停車，而是繼續開行至定遠站才疏散乘客。現場拍到的片段顯示，高鐵冒出濃濃黑煙，更冒出火光。<br />\n<br />\n鐵道部門指出，這列高鐵有16個車廂，共載有1,400人，事故是2號車廂的電器設備發生故障冒煙，事故未造成傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516860632_752d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516860632_752d.jpg&h=035518cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516858954_7acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516858954_7acb.jpg&h=3ccaf176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516861225_7b50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516861225_7b50.jpg&h=29f806d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516861227_58b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516861227_58b3.jpg&h=27423784&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0546913fd7419592cb12f37849be6e4650a644c","tid":540070,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"如果係香港段隧道著火就......"},{"pid":"044fc21199e298e13d24eec233d397a93976f296","tid":540070,"uid":55732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f0546913fd7419592cb12f37849be6e4650a644c","tid":540070,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"如果係香港段隧道著火就......"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"話撚知佢啦，香港人都唔撚會搭<br />\n<br />\n頂多變串燒蝗蟲啫"},{"pid":"faef405dfde1aaa90a2287a1389ab96da0c469a7","tid":540070,"uid":22114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0546913fd7419592cb12f37849be6e4650a644c","tid":540070,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"如果係香港段隧道著火就......"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T08:55:54.000Z","msg":"所以要清拆菜園村起石崗車廠"},{"pid":"8694c085458a2b596495f91043d2c3798cbbf567","tid":540070,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"極速沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b99bf8b654b059b9ef4edc314048d554acbcfb8","tid":540070,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor